Steve Mackall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steve_Mackall 0 Stephen "Steve" Mackall (born December 9, 1959) is a Canadian-American voice-over announcer, voice actor, and screenwriter,. He was known as the voice of NBC's Must See TV", and performed voice of the lead character of Marsupilami in both the Disney animated television series Raw Toonage (1992) and Marsupilami (1993).
